{"tid":621031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不留電子足跡】避公安監控 抗爭者趙思樂：香港人點解會用支付寶？","createTime":"2018-04-08T03:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T15:32:12.000Z","uid":20058,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cd56e85ed0db329fc544a17d7cf1471f886a6b43","tid":621031,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"趙思樂，27歲，廣州人，自小以香港的電視汁撈飯，愛看TVB的專業人士劇集。南京大學金融工程系畢業後，卻跑到女權運動、維權新聞的最前線，曾獲五項香港人權新聞獎、亞洲出版協會（SOPA）卓越新聞獎。新書《她們的征途》寫中國女性抗爭者。近日來港一遊，<span style=\"color: red;\">卻發現香港的姊妹偏愛淘寶，愛屋及烏愛埋支付寶：「台灣人都有少少抵抗，冇諗過香港人一下子就接受咗。可能大家覺得，唔係做政治嘢就冇事。但你好難想像，佢以後點控制你。」 </span><br />\n  <br />\n為免抗爭事業早夭，趙思樂盡量不留下電子足跡。當日雨傘運動一爆發，一張影印店的發票，輾轉就令她的前夫、<span style=\"color: red;\">以至超過100名NGO工作者一網成擒，只因發票系統跟公安搭上了</span>。監控無處不在，翻牆管道也不過是中共預設的狗窿吧？「唔可以一下子話所有技術都冇用。咁係一種偷懶、唔做事的藉口。我哋盡量用專業、安全的方式，繼續工作。」 <br />\n<br />\n立即按此連結Download《壹週刊》: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/NVySCK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FNVySCK&d=XaOglLrVJ8sLvttZ8K56Zy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5c6a3b4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/NVySCK</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180408/2_580703_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F2_580703_0&d=XaOglLrVJ8sLvttZ8K56Zy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=bb6f4a4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F2_580703_0&h=99530342\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180408/2_580703_0</a>"},{"pid":"2914953eda6aa75be6f7e1d5d2f48541153e8052","tid":621031,"uid":26752,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:32:40.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔用支那寶同v7"},{"pid":"4fa88ebc3da44770c921dc6de01d4dedde8305ea","tid":621031,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:36:58.000Z","m